rice exporter in 2011, shipped 2.87 million metric tons from the
beginning of the year to June 14, according to the  Vietnam Food
Association .  Shipments were 329,803 tons from June 1 to June 14, the
association said in a statement on its website today.  Vietnam, which exported a record 7.11 million tons in 2011,
according to the association, may ship 6.25 million tons this
